nodes.title: lora
widgets_values:
14B speedup lora doesn't support 1.3B main model

merge_loras off:
Same result for using WanVideo Set LoRAs Node or linking directly to lora slot of WanVideo Model Loder.

merge_loras on:
is only for linking directly to the lora slot of the WanVideo Model Loader and achieves a different (maybe better) result from merge_loras off.

Tune lora and lora str:
Use WanVideo Set LoRAs Node and turn off merge_loras without loading main model repeatly.

Fixed lora and test merge_loras on:
link directly to lora slot of WanVideo Model Loder and turn on merge_loras.

Wan Video Torch Compile Settings is disconnected by default and will not take effect if you're using fp8 e4m3 diffusion model and your graphic card is 20xx or 30xx.

If you choose fp32/bf16/fp16/fp8 e5m2 model, then you can:
1. Link Wan Video Torch Compile Settings to the Wan Video Model Loader to speed up about 15%~25%..
2. Follow the VRAM settings instruction in the Wan Video Wrapper Tips Group.

Radial attention Resolution
Closest valid sizes for block size 128:
  480x832  -> 512x768
  544x960  -> 512x896
  720x1280 -> 768x1280
Closest valid sizes for block size 64.
  480x832  -> 512x832
  544x960  -> 576x1024
  720x1280 -> 704x1216

choose sparse sage attention:
select sageatten in the Model Loder and bypass the Set Radial Attention.
choose radial sage attention:
select radial_sage_attention in the Model Loder and select sageatten in the Set Radial Attention.

The speed of Radial SageAttn is faster than the Sparse SageAttn.

choose seed generation method:
1. fixed pre-set seed
2. increment based on pre-set seed
3. decrement based on pre-set seed
breake the seed link if you want randomize seed.

nodes.title: Bug
widgets_values: If you link the loop scheduler list combo to the scheduler of WanVideoSampler, the steps will become the default value of 30.

single target: multitalk or infinite single
multi targets: multitalk or infinite multi

nodes.title: Supports up to 12 scene cuts (0-11) by default.
Loop 1 Positive
widgets_values: Medium close-up, static shot, as if from across the tent. a female Knight leans over a large parchment map on a wooden table, her expression serious. Armor is partially unlaced. A single lantern illuminates her face, casting long shadows. Epic fantasy art, dramatic lighting.
use color match as a temporary method to maintain color consistency when using low-step lora.
sometime only the first loop video can be generated and saved. Save images as well.

Sometimes Wan Wapper needs several frames to warm up before normal output, especially for ref2v.
Wan Video length is n*4+1 frames, which might differ from settings. 

multi | infinite talk fps = 25

nodes.title: Loop 2 Positive
widgets_values: Wide shot. The scene is a female Knight holding her first sword in a sunlit cathedral. The mix of awe, pride, and determination shows on the female knight's face. Coming-of-age theme. Epic fantasy art, dramatic lighting.

nodes.title: Loop 5 Positive
widgets_values: An over-the-shoulder shot slowly pushes in toward an illuminated manuscript on a wooden desk, the female knight‚Äôs armored figure in the foreground shimmering softly in the light; as the camera advances, it tilts slightly downward and drifts to the right, reframing her gauntleted hand as it gently traces a line of delicate script before turning the page with deliberate care; she leans forward, her braid slipping over her shoulder as a quiet breath fogs the edge of the parchment, while golden sunbeams pour through a high window, scattering dust motes that swirl around her subtle movements, creating an atmosphere of intellectual focus and serene strength, rendered in epic fantasy art, dramatic lighting.

nodes.title: Loop 7 Positive
widgets_values: A fluid Steadicam shot follows the female knight‚Äôs point of view as she cautiously advances into a vast bioluminescent cavern, the camera gliding forward while tilting upward to reveal glowing stalactites and drifting spores, then subtly drifting side to reframe her line of sight; her armored hand tightens on the hilt of her sword as her breathing quickens, her head turning slightly as her wide eyes reflect the radiant form of a magical creature emerging from the shimmering glow; the ethereal light ripples across her faceplate and catches in the mist, dust motes swirling as the lens pushes closer in rhythm with her hesitant steps, creating a dreamlike, epic fantasy art, dramatic lighting.

nodes.title: Loop 9 Positive
widgets_values: A close-up shot tracks the scarred but capable hands of a female knight as she hammers a dent from her pauldron, the camera pushing in from the side at a low angle before circling slightly to catch the glint of sparks that burst outward with each strike; the lens shudders subtly with the hammer‚Äôs impact, while glowing embers arc across the frame and fade into the blurred rustic background; she adjusts the armor piece with her gauntlet, wipes sweat from her wrist onto her tunic, then raises the hammer again in a steady rhythm, the flickering firelight and hard side illumination carving dramatic highlights across the weathered steel, creating a richly textured, epic fantasy art, dramatic lighting.

nodes.title: Loop 4 Positive
widgets_values: A sweeping wide shot captures a lone female knight standing as a small yet formidable silhouette and guarding the center of a narrow stone bridge at twilight, the vast valley stretching below and a glowing village flickering in the distance; the camera begins with a slow aerial push forward and pass her, emphasizing her isolation against the monumental landscape, before dipping closer to catch the glint of light on the tip of her sword as she shifts her stance, tightening her grip and lowering her shoulders in readiness; her blue surcoat flutters in the rising evening wind, while dramatic sidelight from the fading sun carves her figure into the encroaching dusk, creating an epic fantasy art, dramatic lighting.

nodes.title: Loop 6 Positive
widgets_values: A sweeping wide shot with a slow circling crane movement glides around a female knight seated by a campfire at night, the camera rising and dipping as it orbits slowly to reveal her profile against the star-strewn sky; she shifts her posture, resting her gauntleted hands on her knees before extending one toward the flames, the firelight flickering across her face and polished armor as sparks drift upward; she lifts her gaze to the heavens, her expression softening with quiet wonder, while the embers cast warm orange tones that contrast with the cool blue of the starlit night, the dynamic crane orbit and subtle motions weaving an epic fantasy art, dramatic lighting.

nodes.title: Loop 8 Positive
widgets_values: A dramatic low-angle shot begins from the rain-slick stones of a courtyard, the camera pushing upward slowly from the blurred silhouette of a fallen rival in the foreground to full body of a female knight, her figure outlined against the storm-darkened sky; as the lens slowly rises and arcs in a half-circle orbit, rain cascades down her dented armor, droplets sliding from her gauntlet as she tightens her grip on her sword and exhales heavily, her chest rising with controlled resolve; she shifts her stance, boots splashing in shallow puddles, while thunder rumbles faintly in the distance, the grey sky splitting with shafts of cold light that sculpt her stoic expression, amplifying the emotionally charged epic fantasy art, dramatic lighting.

nodes.title: Loop 10 Positive
widgets_values: Cinematic shot begins as a slow push-in on a rain-streaked cottage window, using a long lens to compress the garden. Inside the frame, a female Knight gently places a wreathe of white flowers before a simple stone marker. As the camera cranes down slightly, she removes a gauntlet to softly touch a blooming rose on the vine, her shoulders relaxing in a moment of quiet sorrow and peace. The golden light of a setting sun breaks through the clouds, casting long shadows and creating a dramatic, poignant atmosphere. Epic fantasy art, dramatic lighting.

nodes.title: Loop 0 Positive
widgets_values: A low-angle slow dolly shot combined with a slow orbit circles upward around a full-body portrait of a proud female knight at dawn, her intricate plate armor gleaming beneath a flowing blue surcoat, her long red braid swaying as she steps forward with resolve, raising her gauntleted hand slightly and slowly while her chest lifts in a deep breath of determination; the golden sunrise breaks through the misty valley behind her, beams of light catching on her armor and hair, as dramatic side light sculpts her figure, with the dynamic camera push and orbit amplifying the epic fantasy art, dramatic lighting.

nodes.title: Loop 3 Positive
widgets_values: A chaotic handheld tracking shot combined with a slow orbit circles upward around at a female knight in the middle of a brutal melee, her dented and mud-streaked armor glinting under flashes of dramatic side light as she ducks and pivots beneath a monstrous axe swing, her braid whipping through the air; the camera jolts and sways with her momentum, pushing in close as her sword slashes upward in a powerful counterattack, motion blur and flying sparks amplifying the chaos, while blurred silhouettes of clashing warriors and the flicker of firelight in the misty battlefield background create a visceral, high-energy epic fantasy art, dramatic lighting.

nodes.title: Loop 11 Positive
widgets_values: A dynamic low-angle tracking shot, pushing forward slowly, follows a female Knight and her massive warhorse as they battle through a blizzard in a high mountain pass. The knight leans forward in the saddle, one arm shielding her face from the driving snow while the other firmly grips the reins. Her warhorse lowers its head, muscles straining against the fierce wind that whips its mane and tail. In the background, through the swirling snow, the immense, terrifying scale of the frozen peaks is revealed. Epic fantasy art, dramatic lighting.
